longBusinessSummary: ReGen III Corp. operates as a cleantech company in Canada. It owns a portfolio of patented technologies that enable used motor oil re-refineries to produce a higher value product mix of base oils. The company was formerly known as Gen III Oil Corporation and changed its name to ReGen III Corp. in May 2021. ReGen III Corp. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
